2:T708,{"@context":"https://schema.org","@type":"FAQPage","mainEntity":[{"@type":"Question","name":"Is Play.ht better than Suno?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"It depends on your needs. Play.ht scores 7.0 overall while Suno scores 8.0. Play.ht is best for developers needing TTS API and podcast intros and voiceovers, while Suno excels for creating music without instruments and content creators needing custom music."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which is cheaper, Play.ht or Suno?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Play.ht starts at $14.25/mo and Suno starts at $8/mo. Play.ht offers a free plan. Suno offers a free plan. Overall value depends on which features you need."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Can I switch from Play.ht to Suno?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Yes, most users can migrate between these platforms. Both Play.ht and Suno support data import/export. The migration process typically involves exporting your data from one platform and importing it into the other. Some tools also offer migration assistance to make the transition smoother."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"What do users say about Play.ht vs Suno?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"On review platforms, Play.ht holds an overall rating of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10. Suno has an overall rating of 8/10 and ease of use score of 10/10. Users praise Play.ht for high-quality voices and Suno for incredibly easy to use."}},{"@type":"Question","name":"Which should I choose in 2026, Play.ht or Suno?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"In 2026, we recommend Suno for most users based on its overall score and feature set. However, Play.ht remains a strong contender, especially if you prioritize high-quality voices. Try both free trials before committing."}}]}0:{"buildId":"P2JZirFppjRTCRUsq6bTg","rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"$2"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":