6:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Play.ht and Suno share a solid foundation of core features including Multilingual. Where Play.ht pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Text To Speech and Voice Cloning and Api Access and Custom Voices and Real Time, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on these capabilities. On the other hand, Suno uniquely offers Music Generation, giving it an edge for users who prioritize this area. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Play.ht holds an overall score of 7/10 and an ease of use score of 7/10, while Suno scores 8/10 overall and 10/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
7:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Suno comes in at a lower starting price of $8/mo, while Play.ht begins at $14.25/mo. Both platforms offer free plans, which is great for testing before committing. Play.ht's free tier and Suno's free tier each have their own limitations, so it is worth evaluating both to see which free offering better matches your initial needs."}]]}]
